caption:
shopping for a basecamp day pass 👀? you know what to do. link in bio. and don’t forget about the 10% off student discount that runs until the 15th if u wanna be a cool kid and commit to 4 or 8 months of climbing rn. be cool. it’s that easy. 

stay chalky climbers 
🤍your favorite disembodied heads

will you remember that on the 6th day of september the new fall schedule starts? we will.

come join us THIS VERY FRIDAY! (the 6th day of september) @basecampclimbing_qw (basecamp queen west) for our first session of the year!!! 

look around for some awesome and very approachable kids in black UTCC shirts and just give us a poke and we’ll introduce you to everyone :) we’re very cool. we promise (not biased at all as we say this)

okay that’s all. stay chalky <3
xoxo,
your disembodied heads of utcc

ps. the first saturday of every month u can climb at basecamp for 30% off 🤫 sign up using the link in our bio!!

pps. until the 15th if you go in person to basecamp you can get 10% the student price for a 4-month pass and you can buy 2 of them to be used consecutively! That’s the whole school year of climbing at 10% off. that’s a good deal if you ask us.
disoriented? wanna get oriented? we’ll orient you. come to the projector room after class :) we’ll feed u but first come first serve …

wow! look how cool and approachable we are! our
first week back had been a smash hit so far with
top rope @basecampclimbing_bw and bouldering
@basecampclimbing_qw and we’d like to thank
you for coming out and hanging out! if you
haven’t had the chance yet, just know that it’s
never too late to pull up. our climbing sessions
are here to provide you with a low pressure and
unstructured way to make friends and climb with
some new faces. feel free to stop in for just one
session and tap someone with a black UTCC shirt
on the shoulder and we’ll introduce you to the
crew and climb with you! most of us don’t bite.
we just wanna be friends with ya :)
see you tonight at basecamp queen west!
ΧΟΧΟ,
your disembodied heads <3
